## Germplasm Phenotype:
   - [mmdh1-2 mmdh2-1]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;mmdh1-2 mmdh2-1 double mutants have no detectable mitochondrial malate dehydrogenase (MDH) activity and over a 40% reduction in total leaf MDH activity. They also have growth defects under long and short days.
